imdb.plot outline: "Here I Come" is a TV/ Web series about the lives of immigrant from all over the world. Several immigrants emigrate into the UK, US and other countries daily. Some are lucky to integrate smoothly into the system; however a large number of people are not so lucky. We are trying to bring to life the real life stories of immigrants that has never been seen or heard before, This is our chance to get tens of millions of people thinking about what really happens in "the green land." It's going to be intense, excruciating and enthralling all at the same time! It will keep you at the edge of your sits...
